name: W3Champions
summary: W3Champions is the ladder made by and for the community. It adds many new and old features to the game, such as a sophisticated matchmaking system, updated map pools, custom hotkeys and various QoL improvements.

name: W3dge
summary: W3DGE is a fast-paced, minimalist arcade game about swallowing wedges before they can stab into you. The walls are closing in and the wedges are lined up endlessly in every direction. How long can you survive?
